
'''Tomas Lutuli Brickhill''' (yavutse ku ya 25 Werurwe 1978), ni umukinnyi wa firime, umwanditsi, akaba n'umucuranzi muri [[Zimbabwe]] .   Yayoboye filime yamenyekanye cyane muri 2017 muri ''Cook Off'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 25 Werurwe 1978 i Londere mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] . Se, Paul Brickhill yahoze ari umusirikare wa Zimbabwe (ZIPRA) akaba n'umuvuzi w'abasirikare. Kubera iyo mpamvu, yari mu buhungiro mu [[Bwongereza]] icyo gihe Tomas yavutse. Ariko, nyuma gato y'ubwigenge bwa [[Zimbabwe]], umuryango wasubiye muri [[Zimbabwe]].  Nyuma yo kugaruka, ise yayoboye ibihangano n’umuco byiswe 'The Book Café'. Se amaze gupfa muri 2014, Tomas ayoboye Café.  Afite abavandimwe batatu: Liam, Amy na Declan.  Yize mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Prince Edward, Harare kuva 1991 kugeza 1996. 

== Umwuga ==
Yavuye muri [[Zimbabwe]] mu 1997 yimukira mu [[Bwongereza]] maze yiga muri Surrey Institute of Art ; Design, Ishuri Rikuru rya Kaminuza mu 1999.  Yize Filime nyuma akora imirimo itandukanye agerageza kunguka ubumenyi butandukanye muri Surrey arangiza na Bachelor of Arts (BA) muri Cinematography na Film / Video Production muri 2001. Hanyuma yigishije amasomo ya firime ya Raindance Film Festival, BBC na VMI imyaka mike. 

Yatunze kandi Paw Paw Jam Productions, isosiyete ikora ibijyanye n’umuziki nyafurika ndetse no gufata amashusho mu [[Bwongereza]].  Usibye sinema, ni n'umucuranzi aherekejwe n'itsinda 'Chikwata'. 

